tspan.tspan: Adv to Perc. checks w/those senses
Advantage on attack roll against a creature if an
ally is within 5 ft. of the creature and is not incapacitated

text.tspan: Detect evil or good. know location & type (but not
ID) of any celestial, fiend, or undead w/i 60' not
behind total cover. Also detect presence of any
1 visible, frightenable foe w/i 60' makes WIS save
Fail = foe is frightened for duration (speed 0)
Succeed = foe's speed is halved for duration
